{
  "id": "65c9c527ef3f6700245215db",
  "title": "線型空間の普遍性",
  "created": 1707722023,
  "updated": 1707722255,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "65c9c527ef3f6700245215db",
      "text": "線型空間の普遍性",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000077a559",
      "text": "from [そこそこまあまあ精密に読む『ベーシック圏論 普遍性からの速習コース』]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000056285f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000008fa08c",
      "text": "[線型空間]の台集合[$ V]が[$ S]で添え字づけられた基底[$ \\bm e_\\bullet:S\\to V]を持つとする。以下が成り立つ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000f5a8b2",
      "text": " [$ \\forall W\\forall f:S\\to W\\exists!\\bar f:V\\to W.f=\\bar f\\circ \\bm e_\\bullet\\land\\bar f\\text{は線型写像である}]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000a4988e",
      "text": "  ただし、[$ W]は線型空間の台集合とする",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000b1caa8",
      "text": " [https://scrapbox.io/files/65c5da39a748fa0025b3b7e6.svg]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000497776",
      "text": "  もっと大きな図のほうがいいかな？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000c5f0de",
      "text": " [ええー？ほんとにござるかぁ？][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000005cafb8",
      "text": " 成り立つ例",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000d0d00e",
      "text": "  例えば[$ f:S\\ni i\\mapsto 2\\bm e_i\\in V]がある",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000078104e",
      "text": "   簡単のため[$ W=V]とした",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000fc2564",
      "text": "  線型写像[$ \\bar f:V\\ni\\bm v\\mapsto2\\bm v\\in V ]を使えば、[$ f=\\bar f\\circ\\bm e_\\bullet]となる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000077ff52",
      "text": "   [$ \\because\\bar f\\circ\\bm e_\\bullet(i)=\\bar f(\\bm e_i)=2\\bm e_i]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000ae501e",
      "text": "  [$ f]に線型性は要求されないのか？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000005d65a6",
      "text": "   たとえば[$ W=V,f:S\\ni i\\mapsto 2\\bm e_i+\\bm e_1\\in V]としてみる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000568550",
      "text": "    [$ S=\\{0,1,\\cdots,N-1\\}]とした",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000c7f1e6",
      "text": "    基底の線型結合は[$ V]に属する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000000136af",
      "text": "   このとき[$ \\bar f(\\bm e_i)=2\\bm e_i+\\bm e_1]となる線型写像[$ \\bar f]が存在すればいいが、存在するとは思えない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000008fc933",
      "text": "    [$ \\bar f:\\bm v\\mapsto 2\\bm v+\\bm e_1]は非線型なので却下",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000d4716e",
      "text": "     [$ \\bar f(a\\bm e_0+b\\bm e_1)=2a\\bm e_0+(2b+1)\\bm e_1]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000001caa94",
      "text": "     [$ a\\bar f(\\bm e_0)+b\\bar f(\\bm e_1)=2a\\bm e_0+(a+3b)\\bm e_1]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000032d21",
      "text": "    いや、↓ならいける",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000002b7cf4",
      "text": "     [$ \\bar f:V\\ni \\bm v\\mapsto\\begin{dcases}2\\bm v+\\bm e_1&\\text{if }\\exist i\\in S.\\bm v=\\bm e_i\\\\\\sum_iv_i\\bar f(\\bm e_i)&\\text{otherwise}\\end{dcases}\\in V]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000333a57",
      "text": "      ここで、[$ v_i]は[$ \\bm v]の基底[$ \\{\\bm e_i\\}_{i\\in S}]における成分とした",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000001879df",
      "text": "       [$ \\bm v=v_0\\bm e_0+v_1\\bm e_1+\\cdots+v_{n-1}\\bm e_{n-1}]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000002cdec",
      "text": "     証明",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000b80cbd",
      "text": "      otherwiseの方で線型写像の定義を満たせている",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000b8b3ee",
      "text": "      [$ \\bar f(\\bm e_i)=2\\bm e_i+\\bm e_1=f(i)]だから[$ \\bar f\\circ\\bm e_\\bullet=f]も満たしている",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000093543c",
      "text": "   [$ f:i\\mapsto\\bm 0]はどうだ？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000002730ad",
      "text": "    これは簡単。[$ \\bar f:\\bm v\\mapsto\\bm 0]とすればいいだけ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000103499",
      "text": "証明",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000007aceeb",
      "text": " [$ f]が非線型でも成り立つことを示したときの[$ \\bar f]の構成法を使えば示せる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000ef305f",
      "text": " 存在を示す",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000004107bf",
      "text": "  [$ \\forall f:S\\to W]にて",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000001f1f4d",
      "text": "   [$ \\bar f]を定義する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000007206f7",
      "text": "    [$ \\bar f:V\\ni \\bm v\\mapsto\\sum_iv_if(i)\\in W]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000d1fb95",
      "text": "     上では場合分けしていたが、線型結合だけで十分だと気付いた[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000673c06",
      "text": "   [$ \\bar f]が線型であることを示す",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000009e4343",
      "text": "    [$ \\forall\\bm v_a,\\bm v_b\\in V\\forall a,b\\in K;]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000505130",
      "text": "       [$ K]は[$ V]に付随する係数体とした",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000f9c530",
      "text": "     [$ \\bar f(a\\bm v_a+b\\bm v_b)=\\bar f(av_{ai}\\bm e_i+bv_{bi}\\bm e_i)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000006f3b6c",
      "text": "          [$ = \\sum_iav_{ai}f(i)+\\sum_ibv_{bi}f(i)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000d12c40",
      "text": "           [$ \\because ][$ \\bar f]の定義",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000000fe05b",
      "text": "           [$ v_{ai},v_{bi}]を[$ \\bm v_a,\\bm v_b]の成分とした",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000b6b8a1",
      "text": "          [$ = a\\sum_iv_{ai}f(i)+b\\sum_iv_{bi}f(i)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000d18181",
      "text": "          [$ = a\\bar f(\\bm v_a)+b\\bar f(\\bm v_b)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000075a5f9",
      "text": "           [$ \\because\\bar f(\\bm v_\\bullet)=\\sum_iv_{\\bullet i}f(i)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000329ee4",
      "text": "    [$ \\therefore\\forall\\bm v_a,\\bm v_b\\in V\\forall a,b\\in K.\\bar f(a\\bm v_a+b\\bm v_b)=a\\bar f(\\bm v_a)+b\\bar f(\\bm v_b)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000005ae55f",
      "text": "  [$ \\therefore\\forall f:S\\to W\\exists\\bar f:V\\to W.f=\\bar f\\circ \\bm e_\\bullet\\land\\bar f\\text{は線型写像である}]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000fa2d7f",
      "text": " 一意性を示す",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000f5e67a",
      "text": "  [$ \\forall f:S\\to W\\forall \\bar f_0,\\bar f_1:V\\to W.]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000dbb05b",
      "text": "   [$ \\begin{dcases}f=\\bar f_0\\circ\\bm e_\\bullet=\\bar f_1\\circ\\bm e_\\bullet\\\\\\bar f_0,\\bar f_1\\text{は線型写像である}\\end{dcases}]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000184050",
      "text": "   [$ \\implies\\forall\\bm v\\in V.]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000004104a8",
      "text": "      [$ \\bar f_0(\\bm v)=\\sum_iv_i\\bar f_0(\\bm e_i)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000ff0f93",
      "text": "         [$ \\because\\bar f_0\\text{は線型写像である}]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000e6d846",
      "text": "        [$ =\\sum_iv_i\\bar f_1(\\bm e_i)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000425978",
      "text": "         [$ \\because f=\\bar f_0\\circ\\bm e_\\bullet=\\bar f_1\\circ\\bm e_\\bullet]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000fa5c98",
      "text": "        [$ =\\bar f_1(\\bm v)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000006cd0f0",
      "text": "         [$ \\because\\bar f_1\\text{は線型写像である}]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000034131a",
      "text": "   [$ \\iff\\forall\\bm v\\in V.\\bar f_0(\\bm v)=\\bar f_1(\\bm v)]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000eb63ef",
      "text": "   [$ \\iff \\bar f_0=\\bar f_1]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000706c1e",
      "text": " [$ \\underline{\\therefore\\forall f:S\\to W\\exists!\\bar f:V\\to W.f=\\bar f\\circ \\bm e_\\bullet\\land\\bar f\\text{は線型写像である}\\quad}_\\blacksquare]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000653365",
      "text": " やったー！証明できた！[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000864404",
      "text": " 一意性の証明で[$ \\bar f]の定義を一ッッッッッ切使っていないことに注目",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000adc3b1",
      "text": "  このことは補題0.3と共通する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000023bd95",
      "text": "この例では、[$ \\bm e_\\bullet]によって、全単射[$ {\\cal F}:(S\\to W)\\to(V\\to W)]が構成できることを示している",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000a530e7",
      "text": " [$ \\cal F]の構成が普遍性を意味している",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c60f1280f00000744c55",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722255,
      "updated": 1707722255
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000067e954",
      "text": "code:eg0.4.tikz(tex)",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f000000045bf2c",
      "text": " \\usepackage{bm}",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000406a68",
      "text": " \\begin{document}",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000007eddf5",
      "text": " \\begin{tikzpicture}[auto,->]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f00000005310d2",
      "text": " \\node (S) at (2,0) {$S$};",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
      "id": "65c9c5271280f0000000ba0dbb",
      "text": " \\node (V) at (0,0) {$V$};",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1707722023,
      "updated": 1707722023
    },
    {
